      <h2 class="font-extrabold lg:text-4xl text-3xl pt-10">How can this help me?</h2>
      <div class="max-w-lg mt-6 prose prose-indigo dark:prose-invert">
        <p>
          If your new to Karting you can explore all the UK Tracks, browse the basic information and check out when the next events are inc Test Days and Race Days. You'll also be able to see what Championships are running and when.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you're already part of the Karting community you can still get all the information you need to plan your next visit to the track. You can also follow your favourite tracks, championships and events and view them all on your own calendar via the User Dashboard.
        </p>
        <p>
          For now, Signing up for an account is free and will give you access to all the features KartStream has to offer. You can also help us by submitting any data corrections you may find.
        </p>
        <div class= "grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
          <div class="p-4 space-x-4 flex justify-center">
            <%= link_to events_path, class: "btn btn-primary font-medium text-white dark:text-white flex items-center group mb-5" do %>
              View Events Calendar
            <% end %>
            <% unless user_signed_in? %>
              <%= link_to "Sign Up for an Account", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-primary font-medium text-white dark:text-white flex items-center group mb-5" %>
            <% end %> 
          </div>   
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lg:w-1/2 w-full">
      <%= image_tag "jhphoto-3117.webp", alt: "Challenges", class: "max-w-full h-auto w-full" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-800 to-slate-900 text-white">
