      <h3 class="text-white font-extrabold text-3xl my-2">Organise your Season</h3>
      <div class="prose prose-indigo text-white max-w-lg">
        <p>
          KartStream is your go-to source for up-to-date karting events. Our platform meticulously compiles and presents a wide array of events, from local test and race days to major championships across the UK. With just a few clicks, you can access detailed informatiom, ensuring you're always in the know about upcoming karting events. Planning your next race or visit to the track has never been easier.
          </p>
          
          <h4 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">Follow and Connect with Your Karting World</h4>
          <p>
          But KartStream is more than just a calendar. It's a dynamic community hub where you can follow your favorite events, championships, and tracks. Stay engaged with the karting world by getting regular updates and notifications about the events you care about. Whether you're tracking the progress of specific championships or keeping an eye on your local track, KartStream keeps you connected and informed.

          Join the KartStream community today and elevate your karting experience. Stay ahead with our comprehensive schedules and engage with the events and tracks that fuel your passion for karting.
        </p>

        <p>Join the KartStream community today and elevate your karting experience. Stay ahead with our comprehensive schedules and engage with the events and tracks that fuel your passion for karting</p>
